1. script for importing keys and fingerprints from pidgin.. into otrtalk..
   safer than pointing otrtalk profile to pidgin files!


2. additional commands for managing buddies and keys

otrtalk buddy list
otrtalk buddy info [buddy]
otrtalk buddy add [alias] [id]
otrtalk buddy remove [alias]

otrtalk key generate accountname protocol
otrtalk key list
otrtalk key find accountname protocol
otrtalk key import accountname protocol filename/json/
otrtalk key export

